title: Navy boyfriend gets shipmates onboard with Valentine's message | Central
text:
Photo of the heart-shaped message Credit: Joe Tolster A Birmingham man, who is away with the Navy on a nine month tour, has got his shipmates onboard to help with a Valentine's message for his girlfriend.
Joe Tolster has 3 months left, and wanted to show his girlfriend Alex Reeves he is thinking of her.
 West Midlands Birmingham Valentine's Day
